release.name: v1.13.0
release.body:
## What's Changed
* Update changelog for v1.12.3 by @wu-clan in https://github.com/fastapi-practices/fastapi_best_architecture/pull/1009
* Update the JWT for easier scaling by @wu-clan in https://github.com/fastapi-practices/fastapi_best_architecture/pull/1011
* Update the database and Redis for easier scaling by @wu-clan in https://github.com/fastapi-practices/fastapi_best_architecture/pull/1015
* Fix database calls in init CLI command by @wu-clan in https://github.com/fastapi-practices/fastapi_best_architecture/pull/1016
* Fix install plugin dependencies in docker container by @wu-clan in https://github.com/fastapi-practices/fastapi_best_architecture/pull/1017
* Fix database engine in auto init CLI command by @wu-clan in https://github.com/fastapi-practices/fastapi_best_architecture/pull/1018
* Rename locale to locales to avoid library conflict by @wu-clan in https://github.com/fastapi-practices/fastapi_best_architecture/pull/1021
* Optimize dynamic config loading implementation by @wu-clan in https://github.com/fastapi-practices/fastapi_best_architecture/pull/1022
* Optimize i18n language file directory structure by @wu-clan in https://github.com/fastapi-practices/fastapi_best_architecture/pull/1023
* Fix snowflake type primary key field serializer by @wu-clan in https://github.com/fastapi-practices/fastapi_best_architecture/pull/1024
* Optimize code generation data processing by @wu-clan in https://github.com/fastapi-practices/fastapi_best_architecture/pull/1020
* Update the i18n file storage directory by @wu-clan in https://github.com/fastapi-practices/fastapi_best_architecture/pull/1027
* Bump dependencies and pre-commits by @wu-clan in https://github.com/fastapi-practices/fastapi_best_architecture/pull/1029
* Fix custom filename in code generation by @wu-clan in https://github.com/fastapi-practices/fastapi_best_architecture/pull/1030
* Add router jinja template for code generation by @wu-clan in https://github.com/fastapi-practices/fastapi_best_architecture/pull/1031
* Allow to add config in plugin toml by @wu-clan in https://github.com/fastapi-practices/fastapi_best_architecture/pull/1033
* Refactor code generation and plugin hot reloading by @wu-clan in https://github.com/fastapi-practices/fastapi_best_architecture/pull/1032
* Add injection app routes to code generation by @wu-clan in https://github.com/fastapi-practices/fastapi_best_architecture/pull/1034
* Remove deprecated parameter for code generation business by @wu-clan in https://github.com/fastapi-practices/fastapi_best_architecture/pull/1035
* Add code generation preview mode CLI command by @wu-clan in https://github.com/fastapi-practices/fastapi_best_architecture/pull/1036
* Update plugins and adapt to new features by @wu-clan in https://github.com/fastapi-practices/fastapi_best_architecture/pull/1040
* Add data validator for plugin config by @wu-clan in https://github.com/fastapi-practices/fastapi_best_architecture/pull/1041
* Fix code generation app route injection by @wu-clan in https://github.com/fastapi-practices/fastapi_best_architecture/pull/1042
* Update the plugin git address pattern by @wu-clan in https://github.com/fastapi-practices/fastapi_best_architecture/pull/1047
* Update plugin and code generation subprocess output by @wu-clan in https://github.com/fastapi-practices/fastapi_best_architecture/pull/1048
* Add the alembic related operation CLI by @wu-clan in https://github.com/fastapi-practices/fastapi_best_architecture/pull/1049
* Update task path resolution and docker variables by @wu-clan in https://github.com/fastapi-practices/fastapi_best_architecture/pull/1050
* Update redis and server health monitor data by @wu-clan in https://github.com/fastapi-practices/fastapi_best_architecture/pull/1051
* Add multi level caching and optimize caching by @wu-clan in https://github.com/fastapi-practices/fastapi_best_architecture/pull/1054
* Add granian and celery metrics collection by @wu-clan in https://github.com/fastapi-practices/fastapi_best_architecture/pull/1057
* Fix relational insertion error for empty lists by @SoulEater in https://github.com/fastapi-practices/fastapi_best_architecture/pull/1056
* Optimize the serialization of join query results by @wu-clan in https://github.com/fastapi-practices/fastapi_best_architecture/pull/1058
* Update alembic and ruff config to pyproject.toml by @wu-clan in https://github.com/fastapi-practices/fastapi_best_architecture/pull/1060
* Add tombi toml and bump pre-commits by @wu-clan in https://github.com/fastapi-practices/fastapi_best_architecture/pull/1061
* Add tombi and plugin JSON schema config by @wu-clan in https://github.com/fastapi-practices/fastapi_best_architecture/pull/1062
* Fix multi level cache key build and usage by @wu-clan in https://github.com/fastapi-practices/fastapi_best_architecture/pull/1066
* Add log mount to docker compose by @yzbf-lin in https://github.com/fastapi-practices/fastapi_best_architecture/pull/1063
* Fix captcha and user validation order logic error by @mic1on in https://github.com/fastapi-practices/fastapi_best_architecture/pull/1065
* Add multi level cache for dynamic config by @wu-clan in https://github.com/fastapi-practices/fastapi_best_architecture/pull/1067
* Add version check and update workflows by @wu-clan in https://github.com/fastapi-practices/fastapi_best_architecture/pull/1068
* Add cache key chaining syntax support by @wu-clan in https://github.com/fastapi-practices/fastapi_best_architecture/pull/1069
* Refactor the interface rate limiter implementation by @wu-clan in https://github.com/fastapi-practices/fastapi_best_architecture/pull/1072
* Fix dynamic config cache serialization by @wu-clan in https://github.com/fastapi-practices/fastapi_best_architecture/pull/1075
* Bump dependencies and pre-commits by @wu-clan in https://github.com/fastapi-practices/fastapi_best_architecture/pull/1076
* Fix missing parent class init in base exception by @wu-clan in https://github.com/fastapi-practices/fastapi_best_architecture/pull/1077
* Update the version number to 1.13.0 by @wu-clan in https://github.com/fastapi-practices/fastapi_best_architecture/pull/1079

## New Contributors
* @SoulEater made their first contribution in https://github.com/fastapi-practices/fastapi_best_architecture/pull/1056
* @mic1on made their first contribution in https://github.com/fastapi-practices/fastapi_best_architecture/pull/1065

**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/fastapi-practices/fastapi_best_architecture/compare/v1.12.3...v1.13.0
